reviews.name: VM Audio SRHP9 Stereo MP3/iPhone iPod Over Head On Ear DJ Headphones - Pink/Grey
reviews.reviewText: I just got 3 of these because I had one b-4. close out for somebody. great sound for me. very comfortable, I have a more expensive set but not near as comfortable to wear. great buy. make sure when u get them, u won't think they work. there is a small volume control wheel on the left ear piece. u have to turn the volume up. took me 3 days to find that on my 1st one. small black wheel. enjoy.
reviews.title: fabulous
